<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Motorola rating cut.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Motorola rating cut.</headline>
<dateline>CHICAGO 1997-07-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>Robertson Stephens on Friday cut its rating on technology giant Motorola Inc to long-term attractive from buy, a market source said.</p>
<p>-- The analyst was not available for comment.</p>
<p>-- The downgrade was based on the high valuation of Motorola shares and the cautious tone sounded at the company's meeting with analysts on Thursday, the source said.</p>
<p>-- Motorola shares were off 3-5/16 at 85-11/16.</p>
<p>((Reuters Chicago Newsdesk (312) 408-8787))</p>
